{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "008b91f3-ca1d-4e9f-a296-6556cba51432", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/008b91f3-ca1d-4e9f-a296-6556cba51432@1.pkg/1772597550757/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597551416", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/008b91f3-ca1d-4e9f-a296-6556cba51432@1.pkg/1772597550757/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597551416"}, "identifier": "008b91f3-ca1d-4e9f-a296-6556cba51432", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查对 &ldquo;走向未来&rdquo; 中如何规划人生、适应社会的理解。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②：航天青年、驻村书记、青年医护等群体的选择，体现了走向未来需要将个人发展与时代需求相结合，在实践中积累经验、提升适应社会的能力，符合 &ldquo;走向未来&rdquo; 中关于要正确把握时代机遇、脚踏实地规划人生的知识点，故①②符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③：&ldquo;只关注眼前机遇，不必为长远发展做准备&rdquo; 错误，走向未来需要兼顾眼前与长远，树立长远发展意识；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④：&ldquo;脱离社会需求，仅凭个人喜好规划人生&rdquo; 错误，人生规划应结合社会需求与个人特点，脱离社会的规划难以真正实现价值；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>故本题选 A。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）青春如火炬，如奔涌的江河，蕴藏着无限的力量与可能。在航天领域，&ldquo;90 后&rdquo; 工程师们接力攻关，让 &ldquo;嫦娥&rdquo; 探月、&ldquo;天问&rdquo; 落火的梦想照进现实；在乡村振兴一线，年轻的驻村书记们扎根田野，用知识与汗水带领村民闯出致富路。这启示我们（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①着眼长远，将个人发展融入时代脉搏</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②脚踏实地，在实践中积累走向社会的经验</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③只关注眼前机遇，不必为长远发展做准备</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④脱离社会需求，仅凭个人喜好规划人生道路</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）青春如火炬，如奔涌的江河，蕴藏着无限的力量与可能。在航天领域，“90 后” 工程师们接力攻关，让 “嫦娥” 探月、“天问” 落火的梦想照进现实；在乡村振兴一线，年轻的驻村书记们扎根田野，用知识与汗水带领村民闯出致富路。这启示我们（ ）①着眼长远，将个人发展融入时代脉搏②脚踏实地，在实践中积累走向社会的经验③只关注眼前机遇，不必为长远发展做准备④脱离社会需求，仅凭个人喜好规划人生道路", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/008b91f3-ca1d-4e9f-a296-6556cba51432@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984730173", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②④</span><span>&nbsp;</span